{
  "texts": [
    "Our work serves as a first complete result in the parity-odd sector for non-unit sound speeds.",
    "See[44] for a discussion of how a parity-odd trispectrum can be generated at loop level.",
    "These two solutions are complex conjugate to each other for both light and heavy fields.",
    "Note that the connected propagator has the same conformal weight as the full bulk-bulk propagator so it remains the case that ψ C n ∼ k 3 by scale invariace.",
    "We stress that the power of the scale factor in Dv is fixed by diffeomorphism invariance (gauge redundancy) rather than scale invariance (isometry), and so is the same for any FLRW spacetime."
  ]
}